# Browser QA

- Use the documented browser path for this repo.
- Prefer isolated Playwright or a documented auth-bypass copy when normal auth blocks agent QA.
- Capture screenshots/traces on failures when available.
- When browser login is required, use the handoff pattern: agent opens page, user logs in, agent resumes.
